# .npmrc — npm configuration for LinkForge
#
# IMPORTANT — devDependencies at build time:
#   Render sets NODE_ENV=production during its build step, which causes plain
#   `npm install` to skip devDependencies. This breaks the build because:
#     - typescript     → required by `npm run build` (tsc)
#     - prisma CLI     → required by `npm run prisma:generate`
#
#   Primary fix: render.yaml buildCommand uses `npm install --include=dev`
#   which explicitly installs devDependencies regardless of NODE_ENV.
#
#   If deploying manually or to another platform without render.yaml,
#   remember to run: npm install --include=dev

